items.title: Awesome Icons
items.content_text:
### Archive of Icons

*   [TheNounProject](https://thenounproject.com/) - Search over 150,000 icons designed by creators from arround the world.
*   [svg-icon (â­1.1k)](https://github.com/leungwensen/svg-icon) - An ultimate svg icons collection done right, with over 4,000 SVG icons out of the box.
*   [icons8](https://icons8.com/) - 63,900 Free Flat Icons.
*   [flaticon](https://www.flaticon.com/) - 1,468,000 vector icons grouped in 30,310 packs.

### Generic

*   [Govicons](http://govicons.io/) - Gov Icons is a font and CSS toolkit with 115 government themed icons.
*   [icoMoon](https://icomoon.io) - 490+ free Icons.
*   [Octicons](https://octicons.github.com/) - All GitHub's icons.
*   [RPG-Awesome](https://nagoshiashumari.github.io/Rpg-Awesome/) - A fantasy themed font and CSS toolkit.
*   [zondicons](http://www.zondicons.com/) - A set of free premium SVG icons for you to use on your digital products.

### Map / Countries

*   [StateFace](http://propublica.github.io/stateface/) - All 50 states plus D.C. and a wee continental U.S. map.

### Social

*   [Zocial (â­189)](https://github.com/adamstac/zocial) - Sass and Compass CSS3 social buttons framework.

### Weather

*   [Weather Icons](https://erikflowers.github.io/weather-icons/) - 222 Weather Themed Icons and CSS.

### Merchants

*   [PaymentFont](http://paymentfont.io/) - A sleek webfont containing 95 icons of all main payment operators and methods.

items.title: Awesome Phalcon
items.content_text:
### Application Skeleton

*   [Webird (â­97)](https://github.com/perchlabs/webird) - Webird was created to merge the latest PHP and Node.js innovations into a single application stack

### CMS & Blogs

*   [Yona CMS (â­368)](https://github.com/alexander-torosh/yona-cms) - CMS based on Phalcon Framework with modular structure

### Config

*   [Phalcon Config Loader for Yaml (â­2)](https://github.com/ienaga/PhalconConfig) - Loads all the yml in the directory of the app/config.

### ORM

*   [phalcon-redis-model (â­16)](https://github.com/ienaga/RedisPlugin) - redis based ORM and Easy Criteria (The correspondence of MySQL sharding.)

### Provisioning

*   [setupify (â­3)](https://github.com/perchlabs/setupify) - A collection of bash scripts for provisioning a Zephir and Phalcon based system for deployement or development

### Routing

*   [Phalcon Routing for Yaml (â­4)](https://github.com/ienaga/PhalconRouter) - Routing can be easily configured with yaml

### E-Books / Communities

*   [Phalcon PDF Documentation](https://buildmedia.readthedocs.org/media/pdf/phalcon-php-framework-documentation/latest/phalcon-php-framework-documentation.pdf) - Phalcon Framework Documentation
